<plot>Daughter of a slave and a white man, Isaura lived in a farm, in Campos do Goitacazes, in the state or Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, being treated as a daughter by Ester, her owner, but as a slave by Commandeur Almeida, Ester's husband. Isaura's first love died in a arson, started by Leôncio, Commandeur Almeida's son and completely obsessed with her. After many misfortunes, Isaura meets Álvaro, an abolitionist.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?181617</url></doc>
